title: You are a Liar!
itunes:title: You are a Liar!
description:
Today on the show we had Swizz Beats and Timberland call in to speak on the recent versuz battles, upcoming battles, partnering with Triller and more. Also, during Charlamagne's "Donkey of the Day" we learn that black men cheat after all, just kidding! But we do learn that Derick Jaxn is a cheater and so much more! at that! Moreover, Angela helps some listeners out during "Ask Yee" and nominates Producer Rikki Hughes for Woman History Month.
